                        <interp inst="t18580222-339-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury.—
<rs id="t18580222-339-punishment-51" type="punishmentDescription">
